            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <p>Azure Active Directory is a comprehensive and highly available identification and access control cloud solution. It combines core directory services,advanced identity governance and application access management. Azure Active Directory also provides a standards-based platform with abundant functions which supports developers in providing access control for applications based on centralized policies and rules.</p>
